OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBank 'optimistic' as it    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fedges closer to summer cut 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Bank of England boss has said it   
OL,6, needs to "see more evidence" that price
OL,7, rises have slowed further before       
OL,8, cutting interest rates.                
OL,10,FAndrew Bailey said he was "optimistic  
OL,11,Fthat things are moving in the right    
OL,12,Fdirection" as rates were held at 5.25%.
OL,14,FHe said the Bank expected inflation,   
OL,15,Fwhich measures the rate prices rise at,
OL,16,Fwould fall "close" to its target level 
OL,17,Fin the next couple of months.          
OL,19,FIt paves the way for an interest rate  
OL,20,Fcut as early as June.                  
